Indian Oil Issues Second Tender to Buy Crude for August Loading

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u
-- 
2011-06-13T10:47:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-13/indian-oil-issues-second-tender-to-buy-crude-for-august-loading.html
Indian Oil Corp., the country’s
biggest refiner, issued its second tender for crude for loading
in August, official documents obtained by Bloomberg News showed.  Last week, the company bought about 4 million barrels of
